No. -.

Bush et al. v. Orleans Parish School Board. Thurgood Marshall, A. P. Tureaud and Constance B. Motley for movants. Lloyd J. Rittiner and James F. Redmond for respondent.

The motion to vacate the order of the United States District Court for the Eastern District of Louisiana of August 31, 1960, is denied.
